    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName><name ref="Ildibertus">Ildiperto</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>bone memorie Rachiperti</persName> riceve da <persName
                            key="#Subdeacons"><name ref="Danihel">Danihel</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Andreas">Andree</name></persName> (…) livellario nomine ad
                        censum perxolvendum (…) idest <rs key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">quinque
                            petiis de terris</rs> illis in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/489" key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions">Stanipagio prope
                            Pontetecto</placeName>, pertenens <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/132"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Emperor/king #Churches #Subdeacons #vassusOf"
                            >Sancti Salvestri</orgName>, quas tu per <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libellum</rs> habis da <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king #vassusOf" ref="#people/3313">Ghisalmari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king #vassusOf">vuasso domni imperatori</rs>, quas ego
                        ipse terre modo ad manus mea abere videor; et est <rs key="#Confinia"
                            >tenentes ipse una petia de terra uno caput</rs> in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, alio caput tenet in <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Gumbertus"
                                >Gumperti</name></persName>, lato uno tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3309" key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >Sancti Romani</orgName>, alio lato tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Priests"><name ref="Natalis"
                                >Natali</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs>; et ille alia petia uno caput tenet in
                            <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Notary"
                                ><name>Teudiprandi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notari</rs>, lato uno tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">Sancte Marie</orgName>, et alio
                        latus tenet in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>; et ille tertia petia uno
                        caput tenet in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>, alio caput tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >Sancti Martini</orgName>, lato uno tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">Sancte Marie</orgName>; et ille
                        quarta petia uno caput tenet in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name>Teudi</name></persName>,
                        lato uno tenet in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> que fuit
                            <persName ref="#people/3304"
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Bishops">Teudilasci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et alio latus tenet in <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> de <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">filii quondam
                                <name>Balderichi</name></persName>; et illa quinta petia ambas
                        capitas et ambas lateras tenet in <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"
                            >Sancti Martini</orgName>; (…). Censo (pro omni censum et iustitia):
                        usque dum vos eas per ipsum libellum abueritis, per singulos annos in mense
                        martio (…) hic Luca ad casa abitationis vestre argentum denarios bonos
                        expendiviles numero sexaginta tantum (…) Pena: argentum soledos triginta
                        (…). <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                                >Adalpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: </ab>
                </div>
